data.description: Welcome to this charming one-story home nestled in the heart of New Braunfels. Boasting four spacious bedrooms and three full baths, this residence offers ample space for comfortable living. As you step inside, you're greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere, with an abundance of natural light illuminating the interior. The heart of the home features a cozy living area, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests.  The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances and ample cabinet space for storage. Recent upgrades include a replaced dishwasher, ensuring convenience and efficiency for everyday use. One of the highlights of this property is the detached casita, providing versatile space for guests, a home office, or a private retreat. The primary suite offers a beautiful en suite bath with a jetted tub. Other notable features include a recently replaced water heater, ensuring reliability and peace of mind for years to come. Outside, you'll find a spacious backyard, ideal for enjoying the beautiful Texas weather or hosting outdoor gatherings. With its convenient location and desirable amenities, this home offers the perfect combination of comfort and convenience. Don't miss your chance to make it yours, book your personal tour today!
